			<td class="wwmp_careers_text_description" align="left" valign="top"><strong>WorldWide Medical Products, Inc. (WWMP)</strong> is looking to expand its sales force throughout the U.S. We are seeking a high-energy, self-motivated individual to join our sales team in either the Philadelphia or New York areas. As a Sales Representative, you will be responsible for developing a client base of customers for WWMP and serve as a liaison between management and customers to resolve any customer issues.
			</td>
