	  <li>Obtain new business and exceed annual territory sales budget each year by presenting new product lines, up selling and seeking out new sources of revenues from clients.</li>
	  <li>Develop and present personalized sales presentations to professional audiences (physicians, laboratory staff, clinics and group practices); demonstrate how WWMP's technical features and services could benefit the practice and help lower the cost of consumable purchases.</li>
