	  <li>Develop and maintain a full business pipeline of prospective clients and assume all territory management in an assigned geographic region.</li>
	  <li>Provide timely and accurate reporting of pipeline, account plans and territory management activities as required.</li>
	  <li>Work closely with Management to develop assigned territory in line with company's objectives.</li>
	  <li>Maintain knowledge of competitors and their presence in assigned territory.</li>
